Posts.Content: I had robotic prostate removal seven years ago.Before surgery my psa was 3.4,gleason was 7 and one biopsy out of 15 was positive.After surgery I was told my cancer was contained to the prostate and the margins were clear.My psa last year was 0.01 and this year a year later it is 0.02.I am real concerned.Should I be?
Posts.Title: Psa post robotic prostate removal
